Q: How can I beautify my URLs?

A: You should use rewrite rules. An example for nginx
(http://sysoev.ru/nginx/):

	rewrite /(.*)/\?(.*)	/index.php?area=$1&$2	last;
	rewrite /(.*)/&(.*)		/index.php?area=$1&$2	last;
	rewrite ^/([a-zA-Z]+)/$	/index.php?area=$1	last;

//

